# PortDiary charts

## Value series
- `total_value` = Σ (`shares × price` per holding), not total invested or cash balance
- Backend: `priceOnDate` must not forward-fill **future** quotes into past dates

## TWR (`attachPerformancePct`)
```javascript
chain *= 1 + (v1 - v0 - cf) / v0   // only when v0 > 0
```
- `cf` = net BUY/SELL cash flow on that date, in display currency
- Single-portfolio % comes from backend; merged all-ports recomputes on frontend in `mergePortfolioHistoriesWithPerformance`

## Merge timelines
```javascript
// ❌ sum only rows that exist on date D — port missing row → value vanishes
// ✅ forward-fill each port to last known value before summing
```

